  <recipient-country code="GB" percentage="100">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ICAI&#x2019;s mandate covers all ODA, whichever department it is spent by. In addition to the Department for International Development, aid-spending departments include the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, the Foreign and Commonwealth Office, the Department of Health, the Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs and cross-government funds such as the Conflict, Stability and Security Fund and the Prosperity Fund. Our mandate does not cover aid spent by the devolved Scottish and Welsh governments.</narrative>
